cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SD 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and semantic parsing. Additionally, the use of a neural component in the proposed model suggests that it may also belong to the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The proposed dynamic-programming algorithm for tractable inference suggests that it may also belong to the sub-category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the use of a novel dependency-based representation suggests that it may also belong to the sub-category of cs.SD (Sound).
